originalText.text: Attorney Delacerna’s office got back to me right away and was scheduled for consultation the next day. She explained what went wrong and laid the best option to solve the problem. One thing I really commend about Attorney Delacerna is she doesn’t push her services to you if you can file it on your own unlike other law offices. I applied for my I-765 again and was approved 3 days after. Thank you Attorney Delacerna and Ms.Pretina for your assistance. ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️5/5

She made me feel comfortable, presented and guided me with my options.
Her dynamic team is like family. They’re very accommodating and ready to assist to my queries.
I have been recommending her to my family and friends.
Thank you Attorney and more power to your Team!

originalText.text:
The Best Immigration Lawyer in Town

Atty. Dela Cerna helped me and my family in our immigration journey and we are forever grateful for her assistance.

She will give you the best advice based on your case and not the run around to get your money. Her fees are reasonable and not outrageous like some other immigration attorneys - I know because i have shopped around. Do not listen to anyone complaining about consultation fee, those types of people are not worth listening to. Entitled much? (IMO: If you can’t afford a consultation fee please google “free immigration lawyers”)

originalText.text: My experience with Delacerna law office has been excellent. Claudette and the entire team are professional and easy to work with. Throughout the years they have always answered any questions I have had and get back to me quickly with any/all information. I always recommend them to anyone seeking legal counsel.

originalText.text:
I had the opportunity to work with Atty Delacerna. Through the years I have been in awe with her craftmanship as an immigration lawyer. I have met many lawyers but none has been up to par with her skills and aptitude of the law. I am grateful that I had the opportunity to learn from her and has been mentored by her in dealing with cases.
There a times that I would think some cases is a lost cause but Atty Delacerna has tremendously showed her knack of finding solutions that helped a lot of people and continues to do so.
She is definitely the best immigration and divorce lawyer in town and her intellect goes beyond it. she defines jane of all trades.
